---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="System News - psychonet" description="System news and updates">
  <div class="section-header">
    <pre>{`
▒▒▒ SYSTEM NEWS ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒`}</pre>
  </div>

  <div class="news-entry">
    <pre class="news-date">2026-02-21  k0bura</pre>
    <p>System is online. psychonet is now running on Astro with
    static builds to GitHub Pages. All sections are operational.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="news-entry">
    <pre class="news-date">2026-02-20  k0bura</pre>
    <p>Initial setup. Migrated old site to the old-site branch.
    New BBS-style frontend is under construction.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="news-entry">
    <pre class="news-date">2026-02-19  k0bura</pre>
    <p>Registered domain. Planning site architecture and content
    structure for project documentation.</p>
  </div>

  <p><a href="/">&larr; back to main</a></p>
</Base>

<style>
  .section-header pre {
    color: #ffcc00;
    background: none !important;
    border: none !important;
    padding: 0 !important;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .news-entry {
    margin: 0.8rem 0;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed #332b00;
  }

  .news-entry p {
    margin: 0.3rem 0 0 0;
  }

  .news-date {
    color: #ffcc00;
    background: none !important;
    border: none !important;
    padding: 0 !important;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
